{"tid":423791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(露出多圖!!!) 港男同2鬼妹上山通宵 [ 迎月 ],  嚇到阿媽報警!!!","createTime":"2017-10-04T07:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T08:04:58.000Z","uid":16697,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a13aa49349de4e6615fc9efe46f958bfb465cd5b","tid":423791,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:53:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171004/bkn-20171004101903451-1004_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171004%2Fbkn-20171004101903451-1004_00822_001.html&d=uBwHMcDZ1EtZCNzkkw%2BSgYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=befcd754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171004/bkn-20171004101903451-1004_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004101903451-1004_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171004134456\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004101903451-1004_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171004134456&h=af152482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171004/photo/bkn-20171004101903451-1004_00822_001_02p.jpg?20171004134456\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171004%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171004101903451-1004_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20171004134456&h=f70b8daa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西貢發生行山失蹤驚魂，一名25歲姓鍾男子，昨日（周二）偕同兩名外籍女友人到西貢東郊野公園行山，並於下午4時許，致電母親報平安，並表示會晚上回家。詎料至今晨零時許仍未返抵家門，且失去聯絡，其母親擔心有意外發生，報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方聯同消防員、民安隊通宵登山搜索，至早上10時許，鍾母終致電聯絡上兒子，證實兒子剛好與友人平安返抵東壩，拯救人員遂與他們接觸，在確認三人身份後，結束一場虛驚。<br />\n<br />\n據鍾向警方稱，昨晚入夜後因山路太黑，擔心迷路，故與友人選擇在山上過夜，直至天亮後才繼續落山，而昨晚是農曆八月十四日，又稱為「迎月」。"},{"pid":"26a45c0d52cf80dfe8b24cbeb13bcc92c06b899c","tid":423791,"uid":134474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:54:39.000Z","msg":"你屌埋我嗰份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 